                            <comment id="289128" author="adilger" created="Sat, 9 Jan 2021 14:39:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The &quot;&lt;tt&gt;lfs setstripe -C&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; (overstriping) feature was added in commit v2_12_53-82-g591a9b4ceb, even though this test was added later.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
